cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper discusses a language for representing reaction rules, which are used in various areas of computer science such as artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic (cs.LO), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
